</header><div class="entry-content" itemprop="text"><h2>&#8230; where you will find resources to help you write, publish and market your book.</h2>
<p><em>New York Times and USA Today bestselling author, voted one of The Guardian UK Top 100 Creative Professionals 2013. Also voted one of the Top 10 Blogs for Writers and one of the Top 10 Blogs for Self-Publishers</em>. <em>As seen at:</em></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-21223" src="https://creativepen-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/AsSeenAt060215-1024x291.jpg" alt="AsSeenAt060215" width="600" height="171" srcset="https://creativepen-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/AsSeenAt060215-1024x291.jpg 1024w, https://creativepen-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/AsSeenAt060215-300x85.jpg 300w, https://creativepen-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/AsSeenAt060215.jpg 1534w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></p>
<h3>Hi, I'm Joanna Penn, an author, just like you, and on this site I share my own lessons from the writing journey.</h3>
<p style="text-align: left;">I have made so many mistakes, I want to try and save you time, money and heartache along the way and so I share articles, video and audio about writing and creativity, publishing options, book marketing and being a creative entrepreneur.</p>
<p>If you want to <strong>search the site</strong>, you can find a Search bar on the side of the Blog, or just go to Google and type it &#8216;the creative penn + how to self-publish' or whatever you are looking for.</p>
<h2>(1) Get started right away with the Author 2.0 Blueprint<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><br />
</span></h2>
<p><a href="www.thecreativepenn.com/blueprint/"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-23833" src="https://creativepen-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/2-4-1024x768.jpg" alt="author blueprint" width="400" height="300" /></a></p>
<p>In this free ebook and video series, I share everything you need to write, publish and market your book, as well as how to make a living with your writing. <a title="author 2.0 blueprint" href="http://www.thecreativepenn.com/blueprint-signup/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Click the image above or here to sign up for your Free Author 2.0 Blueprint</a>.</p>
