<h2>(3) Subscribe to the podcast for free audio interviews. Over 300 available now!</h2>
<p><a href="http://www.thecreativepenn.com/podcasts/"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-20990" src="https://creativepen-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/03/CreativePennPodcastButton_240x2402.jpg" alt="CreativePennPodcastButton_240x2402" width="240" height="240" srcset="https://creativepen-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/03/CreativePennPodcastButton_240x2402.jpg 240w, https://creativepen-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/03/CreativePennPodcastButton_240x2402-150x150.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px" /></a></p>
<h2>(4) For everything I know in handy book packages, check out my books!</h2>
<p><a href="https://www.thecreativepenn.com/books/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-26511 size-large" src="https://creativepen-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/allbooksflat-1024x323.jpg" alt="all non fiction" width="1024" height="323" srcset="https://creativepen-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/allbooksflat-1024x323.jpg 1024w, https://creativepen-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/allbooksflat-300x95.jpg 300w, https://creativepen-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/allbooksflat-768x242.jpg 768w, https://creativepen-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2008/12/allbooksflat.jpg 1534w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></a></p>
<p>You can also find a list of my <a title="recommended books for writers" href="http://www.thecreativepenn.com/books-for-writers/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">recommended books for authors here</a>.</p>
